{
  "title": "RotateOverLifetime",
  "description": "Adds a constant angular acceleration to every live particle each frame (analogous to the legacy `TorqueAffector`). The system's integrate pass advances `rotation` from `rotationSpeed`; this module increments `rotationSpeed` itself. Units: degrees per second². Negative values decelerate spin. GPU-eligible.",
